irssi-prowl - Send Prowl notifications upon new mentions or PMs.


Requirements

    - LWP::UserAgent


Installation

    git clone git://github.com/jk0/irssi-prowl.git
    ln -s ~/path/to/irssi-prowl/irssi-prowl.pl ~/.irssi/scripts/autorun/

    /script load autorun/irssi-prowl.pl
    /set prowl
    /set prowl_api_key <your Prowl API key>
    /set prowl_enabled ON
    /save
